Package ohos.sysappcomponents.contact

Class ContactAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.sysappcomponents.contact.ContactAttributes

  • public class ContactAttributes
extends Object
    Provides contact attributes for contact query.

    You create a ContactAttributes object, set the attributes, and pass it to a query method. The method returns the Contact object matching the attributes.
